1. *Okrenuo* se da bih ga bolje video. (He turned around so that I could see him better.)
2. Kada sam ušao u sobu, ona se *okrenula* prema meni. (When I entered the room, she turned towards me.)
3. *Okreni* se levo na sledećem uglu. (Turn left at the next corner.)
4. Čekao sam dok se situacija nije *okrenula* u moju korist. (I waited until the situation turned in my favor.)
5. On je *okrenut* poslu i retko se viđa sa prijateljima. (He is focused on work and rarely sees his friends.)
6. Moram da *okrenem* broj telefona da bih dobio informacije. (I need to dial the phone number to get information.)
7. Njegova sreća se *okrenula* nakon što je dobio novi posao. (His luck turned around after he got a new job.)
8. *Okrenut* sam ka prirodi i volim da provodim vreme u prirodi. (I am oriented towards nature and I love spending time outdoors.)
9. *Okrenuo* sam stranicu knjige i počeo da čitam novi odeljak. (I turned the page of the book and started reading the new section.)
10. Kada je shvatio da je pogrešio, *okrenuo* se i izvinio. (When he realized he was wrong, he turned around and apologized.)